NPCDialogue.LocalizedString: YOU'LL BE NEEDING SOMETHING WITH A BIT MORE REACH THAN THAT SWORD, LAD!

YOU KNOW, I GET THE FEELING THERE WON'T BE A WEAPON JUST LYING AROUND IN THE SWAMP. @I MEAN, HAVE YOU EVER SEEN A SNAIL ROCKING A CROSSBOW? @I HAVEN'T. @BUT... MAYBE... YOU COULD FIND SOMETHING OUT THERE IN... THE OTHER REALM?
JOT! WELCOME BACK! DID YOU GET WHAT YOU WERE LOOKING FOR?
{120}ADVENTURERS!{100} MAYBE YOU CAN 'ELP US! @OUR HOUSE IS FULL OF FLYING BUGS. @PLEASE KICK OUT THOSE INSECTOID THUGS!
YOU BET WE WILL, SNAIL DUDE!
SQUIRE... YOUR SWORD THERE LOOKS MIGHTY SHARP, BUT... @IF YOU WANT TO WALLOP THOSE BUZZING PESTS@A LONG-RANGE WEAPON WILL SERVE THEE BEST! @URM...THERE MAY BE SOMETHING AROUND HERE...?
A LONG RANGE WEAPON HUH? LET'S TAKE A LITTLE GANDER...

HUH... THERE'S SOMETHING LODGED UNDER THE WATER. @MAYBE I COULD DISLODGE IT... WITH... A LITTLE BIT OF MAGIC...? @I CAN NEVER QUITE GET THIS KIND OF THING TO WORK... @BUT... WELL... @I SUPPOSE THERE'S A FIRST TIME FOR EVERYTHING... @GUYS... UH... MAYBE BEST IF YOU... STOOD BACK...
HOLY GUACAMOLE!!! IT ACTUALLY WORKED!!! @OH... UH... I MEAN...
{125}TADAA!!{100} COOL, HUH? @IT'S A BIG LOG. @NOT REALLY A LONG-RANGE WEAPON... @UNLESS YOU THREW IT.
